Coloration. Head brown. Antenna brown. Thorax pale brown, vittae not distinct. Ground color of abdomen pale yellow. Tergites II–V each with a roughly triangular brown area along anterior margin; tergites VI–VIII each with rounded brown area at anterior margin. Hypopygium brown (Fig. 
7
). Legs brown, apices of all femora with dark brown ring.
